	quest.072EFD249D8F659E.quest_desc: [
		"Going through Chests can be frustrating even just in vanilla minecraft, but with all the items Modded adds, you'll want a single place to see all your items. "
		""
		"Tom's Simple Storage allows for this. The wireless option will make it much easier as you walk around your ever expanding Island."
	]
