	quest.2F0E4FC8E699F8F6.quest_desc: [
		"There are two starter power sources in immersive engineering. "
		""
		"1. The Thermoelectric Generator "
		"or "
		"2. Kinetic Dynamo w/ Windmill"
		"or "
		"3. Kinetic Dynamo w/ Water Wheel"
		""
		"Part of Playing with Immersive is enjoying the Cosmetic's of the mod, so while Thermoelectric Generators with Uranium Blocks and water may be the \"optimal\" power production, Kinetic Dynamo's are pretty. "
	]
	quest.2F0E4FC8E699F8F6.quest_subtitle: "Choose your starter!"
