	quest.6D829A5DFB082A15.quest_desc: [
		"We hope you find our mod pack a fun experience. "
		""
		"The intent of this pack is to be a progression-centric pack. The quests will serve as a guide on how to progress from one Phase to the next. "
		""
		"The end goal is to craft the pack's custom made items as components for creating creative tier items."
		""
		"Getting to the end game, requires progressing through mods in the each phase which will unlock the needed materials for the next phase."
	]
