		"The Coke Oven makes two things for us. "
		""
		"It makes us:"
		"1. Coal Coke (useful later for steel) "
		"and "
		"2. Creosote Oil (uesful now for making treated wood)"
		""
		""
		"And you might want to automate a couple of these, cause we're goonna need lots of that oil..."
	]
